overview: Experience the ultimate in hardcore combat--the Yokohama Deathmatch, a.k.a. the Texas Tornado street fight. It's a six-man tag team deathmatch pitting Cactus Jack, Terry Funk and Mike Awesome against Onita, Tanaka and Kanemura in a no-holds-barred fire-breathing, branding, barbwire bat war!
title: FMW: Yokohama Deathmatch
